schools.name: Dr. Henry A. Wise Jr. High School

data.description: Welcome to this stunning home that offers a perfect blend of elegance, and functionality, nestled in a charming country setting, with an exterior featuring three side brick.  As you step inside the foyer, there is a formal living room and formal dining room to your right. This beautiful home features a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a large center island, a walk-in pantry, and a breakfast nook leading to a large deck ready for relaxing and entertaining guests.    The family room is perfect for creating a cozy atmosphere for family gatherings and relaxing evenings in front of the fireplace.  The main level also features an office, a large laundry area with a front-load washer and dryer, and a half bathroom.  As you enter the upper level you will be amazed by the large foyer where you will find three bedrooms, and a luxurious Owner’s Suite with a separate sitting room, two walk-in closets, and a fabulous en-suite with dual vanities, a roman tub, and an awesome large shower.  One of the bedrooms has a bathroom and ample space for a sitting area perfect for quest.  The walkout basement has an open concept where you will find endless space with a bar for entertainment, a full bathroom, and a bonus/flex room that could be made into a media room or kept as a home gym.  The Marlboro Ridge community is a sophisticated recreational community offering state-of-the-art amenities including parks, playgrounds, tennis courts, a clubhouse, a fitness center, and a community swimming pool.  The Prince George's Equestrian Center and Showplace Arena have an indoor arena, stables, and horseback riding trails and host events throughout the year.  Families who live here will enjoy a relaxed atmosphere of tranquil country living, with excellent shopping/restaurants and a wide selection of cultural and recreational events close to home, minutes from Andrews Air Force Base, the Beltway 495, DC, Virginia, and Annapolis.  The possibilities are virtually endless, and you and your family can be a part of it. Here at Marlboro Ridge.
